In Salesforce Apex, you generate a PDF using a **Visualforce page rendered as PDF**.

---

# 1. Create Visualforce Page (PDF Template)

```xml id="vf1"
<apex:page renderAs="pdf" standardController="Account">

    <h1>Account Report</h1>

    <p><b>Name:</b> {!Account.Name}</p>
    <p><b>Phone:</b> {!Account.Phone}</p>
    <p><b>Industry:</b> {!Account.Industry}</p>

</apex:page>
```
<apex:page standardController="Booking__c" renderAs="pdf">

    <h1>Booking Details</h1>

    <p><b>Booking Name:</b> {!Booking__c.Name}</p>
    <p><b>Booking Date:</b> {!Booking__c.Booking_Date__c}</p>
